author: wn.com
title: Australian-Chinese businessman Michael Li claims China intimidation after refusing to act as spy
text: A prominent Australian-Chinese businessman says China's security agencies have placed his family under surveillance in Sydney and imprisoned his brother in China because he refused to act as a spy for Beijing. ...
